## Cyclist: Constant Angular Acceleration
## Part 1
## By C. Freeman, freeman@NSRL31.NSRL.rochester.edu
## No unauthorized commercial use
## Imported Files
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
